# Production Lock File

This file indicates that the production directory is locked and finalized.

## Lock Date
2024-01-31

## Locked Components
- Core systems (ethics-guard, matrix-engine, analytics-guard, numerology-engine)
- State registry and weight table
- Region profiles
- Audit log schema
- Production shell (index-integrated-ryd.html)
- Tools directory
- Numerology directory (SEO doorway)
- Store directory

## Lock Rules
- No mock, test, or sandbox code in production
- No user-facing matrix references
- Ethics guard has absolute veto
- All systems are bounded, logged, reversible
- Numerology is symbolic only, isolated from matrix
- GA4 is aggregate only, governed by analytics-guard
- Store is passive only

## Modification Policy
- Core systems: Human approval required
- Content: Human approval required
- Weights: Bounded, logged, reversible
- Audit log: Append-only

## Testing
See TESTING.md for test procedures.

## Deployment
Production is ready for deployment when all tests pass.

